# Keep these files tracked (safe):
# - docker-compose.yml (references env vars, no secrets embedded)
# - .env.example (template with placeholder values only)
# - n8n/demo-data/ (example workflows, anonymized)
# - start.sh, stop.sh, switch-model.sh (utility scripts)
# - README.md, CONTRIBUTING.md (documentation)
# - LICENSE (license file)
# - shared/ (shared utilities, no secrets)
# - assets/ (static files)
